We had posted this on the @homebredbygitika a couple of months ago, it was a day when I (Gitika) was cribbing about work & highly demotivated. Zain was giving me a pep talk which turned out to be extremely insightful. Everyone on the Homebred page said they wanted to hear more such talks! So sharing it here in case you’re having one of those days where you feel like nothing is going right & you don’t want to do anything 🤗

Here’s to many more projects to come🥰🧿✨

She’s an advocate, co-founder of a bakery and a model, a Vogue Model. Zainika was born with down-syndrome but that never stopped her from chasing her passion and dreams. She’s wearing Our Rani Udaymati Collection, and it suits her perfectly- the statement designs bring out her confident personality. She’s strong, she’s passionate and her main message to everyone out there is plain and simple- be kind!
